														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2682161">
									

<p>The presentation of this page and Harbinger feel too separate. I'll make a longer post on Harbinger's page, because I love the shit out of that tale, but this feels even more unnecessary than a splash page. A proposal SCP that's actually a hub linking to a tale (with no indication that the tale by itself is even linked to this 001 proposal, unless you're putting the parent on that page as I'm typing this) is novel but it doesn't work as a full-blown proposal, just linking to one tale. There surely must be more to come, because this feels so barebones as it is, though even considering what it will be in the future (if there is more that's being doled out over time), I dunno how I feel about this page itself. It feels like a situation similar to Mann's Proposal, except only one half of it is interesting.</p>

							</div>

								
