			<div class="content" id="post-content-2682396">
									

<p>Far be it from me to be so bold as to decide what form an 001 proposal needs to take, especially if that form fits my expectations of a proposal. Guess you can't expect everybody to feel the same, which is unfortunate.</p>
<p>Regardless, I am overwhelmingly enthused about this. Truthfully, I think I would've been disappointed had it just been a single article, since the entire scope of the &quot;This Dying World&quot; minicanon could not be adequately contained within a single piece, I think.</p>
<p>Goddamn, it's a beautiful day.</p>

